data.description: Charming Country Home on 2.2 flat very usable acres with 3 car garage. Views of Mtns and Wenatchee lights. Acreage is flat with irrigation. Only minutes to downtown Wenatchee and minutes to Ski Hill. Updates throughout. This is a must see to  enjoy the beautiful setting. You have it all.   Room to park whatever you need and besides the 3 car garage room to build your dream shop. You will be in love!!!!
